          "text": "oh, good question!\n---\nit looks like we've got the basic project set up, which is purr-fect! but all our core docs are empty still.\n---\nso, the very first thing we usually nail down is the project's vision. like, what's the big idea here?\n---\nwhat's the one thing you're trying to achieve with this app?\n\n",
