    {
      "id": "rsZyFurOu9p0Gibf",
      "role": "assistant",
      "parts": [
        {
          "type": "step-start"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "aha, a tasks app for doctors! that's a super clear direction.\n---\nis it for managing their *own* tasks, or tasks *for patients* from their team, or something else entirely?\n---\nknowing that will help me start fleshing out the vision spec!\n\n",
