          "type": "step-start"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "both, got it! that makes a lot of sense for a doctor's workflow.\n---\nso, to make sure I capture this vision perfectly, what's the ultimate goal here? like, what problem does this app solve for them, and what does success look like for a doctor using it?\n\n",
