          "text": "oh, a kanban board! like trello, but for doctors. i love that for task management.\n---\nso, are the columns fixed (like \"to-do,\" \"in progress,\" \"done\") or can doctors customize them for their different workflows?\n---\ni'd lean towards customisable columns to give them more flexibility, what do you think?\n\n",
